.\"=============================================================================
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
command was hacked together during a return commute in late November 2017,
driven in large part by the revulsion its author heralded towards contemporary \
Node.js tooling.
Bits and pieces of functionality were added piecemeal over time,
and it wasn't until
.Xr jg-lint 1
was written that a wrapper for the two tools was written and \
a Git repository created,
brashly named after its author's initials.
.
